gazebo-kotlin
=============

A Kotlin Multiplatform port home for primitives from
[facebookincubator/gazebo](https://github.com/facebookincubator/gazebo).
The first ported subtree is `cmp_any`.

Upstream `gazebo` is dual-licensed Apache-2.0 OR MIT, copyright Meta
Platforms. The Kotlin translation here is a derivative work, distributed
under the same dual Apache-2.0 OR MIT terms. All algorithmic and
structural design credit — the type-erased comparator capture pattern
in OrdAny, the `TypeId`-tagged equality in PartialEqAny — belongs to the
upstream contributors.

Vendored Rust source is fetched into `tmp/gazebo/cmp_any/` by
`tools/fetch-rust-source.sh` and is not tracked in this repo.

